      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. If the intrinsic factor is being produced but the B12 levels are still low, could it be an issue with the actual absorption process in the ileum, or is there something else that might be preventing the B12 from being properly utilized or \"kept\" in the system?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
