      "content": "I see. So if we rule out those specific medical conditions and genetic factors, is it possible that the B12 is just \"disappearing\" before it can be fully integrated? Like, could there be some kind of interference where the nutrient is present in the gut but simply fails to be captured or stays \"lost\" in the digestive process?",
